{"tid":2214922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百佳：曾提出以購物八折，或贈送現金券回饋巿民，但不獲政府接納","createTime":"2020-09-23T14:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T16:01:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9279aeba212ca688d61a76e619547def401682","tid":2214922,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"有份獲批保就業計劃的兩大超市集團惠康及百佳，按政府要求為顧客提供優惠。其中百佳除了向弱勢社群發放現金食物券，今日再公布設立總額3200萬的現金券抽獎計劃，市民可透過網上或電話登記，提供手機號碼及身份證頭四個字參加抽獎。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>百佳：提出購物八折遭拒 </strong><br />\n百佳話，曾經向當局提出以購物八折，或贈送現金券給顧客模式，將保就業資助的一半回饋巿民，但不獲政府接納，因此改用抽獎模式回饋。百佳在保就業計劃第二期獲批1.61億，現時已公佈的方案金額約7千多萬。百佳表示，保就業計劃金額當中有一成，即是約1千6百萬，會以現金形式回饋給員工。 預料下月向弱勢社群派發現金食物券<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2358481&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=23963fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358481</a>"},{"pid":"e8b9a07fc08c2e782065bf26c9fd794094031dca","tid":2214922,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"6f4169654cc3668e9bc3d90e6088cac27f1066c9","tid":2214922,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"消息：惠康與7-11便利店合作派餐劵 <br />\n<br />\n惠康昨日亦宣布推出總值超過1.2億元的回饋社會計劃，未來10個月與慈善團體合作，派發200萬張現金劵及餐劵予最有需要的人士。消息指，現金券和餐券各100萬張，惠康會與同集團7-11便利店合作，受助人可以憑餐券到便利店領飯盒，詳情稍後公佈；惠康另外會捐出500萬元幫助弱勢社群，又承諾未來半年，超過300款日常貨品不加價。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2358481&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=23963fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358481</a>"},{"pid":"13adae1288484a0a361486523f3fd52c9a899d78","tid":2214922,"uid":245670,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"幾年無去過百佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f2f6c4745a4d3a58b841a920f417a045756e88","tid":2214922,"uid":260251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20257c126669b3e9f36754a6fea8c110c9fc286c","tid":2214922,"uid":198314,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"8折起碼叫人人有份有優惠<br />\n依加就得小部份人受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f821ea22058c319daece6b8c637e402d1cb99b","tid":2214922,"uid":365024,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e8b9a07fc08c2e782065bf26c9fd794094031dca","tid":2214922,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"Hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"傳染病處主任平時去開百佳定惠康買嘢 聽講鈕祜祿鍾意親自下廚 啲花會種嚟食"},{"pid":"93a6d4a96b8eb7f45df71a2bb5936e1b30eda855","tid":2214922,"uid":124630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"被拒原因係咩"},{"pid":"7ccefd5a81448057b3db00c5411d022aa6c38faf","tid":2214922,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93a6d4a96b8eb7f45df71a2bb5936e1b30eda855","tid":2214922,"uid":124630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"被拒原因係咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"因為惠康如果唔跟 佢會無左人幫襯掛"},{"pid":"7c0062bb7fa2c26dbc249e3a5e1b3150e9449429","tid":2214922,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1568af479892ec9097f13f55f817cbe884d7fc86","tid":2214922,"uid":65747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"20257c126669b3e9f36754a6fea8c110c9fc286c","tid":2214922,"uid":198314,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-